            <h3>Create and Organize Your Creative Constructs</h3>
            <p>Thoughts materialize but are rarely recorded by us. Even rarer do we deliberate on them and upgrade them. Here you can write entire constructs in a powerful editor, store them and keep on upgrading them. Any Creative Constructs or thoughts can be stored indefinitely. Never lose your thoughts again. When thoughts become too many, you can organize them proficiently. Categorize your thoughts according to your preferences, view them at will and upgrade.</p>
            <p><a href="/apropos/how_to_use" class="button-style">Read More</a></p>
          </li>
          <li>
