          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>Record Your Epiphanies, Brainwaves and Factoids</h3>
            <p>Cognition is the mental action or process of acquiring knowledge and understanding through thought, experience, and deliberation. Cognitions are acquired through perception, sensation or intuition. These realizations generally result in the most innovative, intriguing and fascinating thoughts. Cognition is any form of cognitive activity. MentalConstructs has narrowed down "Cognitions" into 3 major subcategories. Epiphanies, BrainWaves and Factoids.</p>
            <p><a href="/apropos/how_to_use" class="button-style">Read More</a></p>
